      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in Clip 1.4.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Recursive Search</strong> — vault search now finds assets nested inside folders at any depth</li>
          <li><strong>Markdown Files</strong> — open .md files from disk, preview rendered, import into vault with MD badge</li>
          <li><strong>SVG Copy & PNG Paste</strong> — copy SVG text assets to clipboard, paste any image as PNG</li>
          <li><strong>Sparkle Auto-Update</strong> — automatic update checking with one-click install</li>
        </ul>
